73
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,510
- A feel? - Well,there's no bugs on him,
- 灵感? - 恩, 在他的身上并没有虫子

74
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,510
haven't been for over a thousand years.
不像是过了上千年的样子

75
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:20,590
There may be spores and pollens,correct?
这儿也许有孢子或是花粉, 对吗?

76
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:21,410
Probably not.
恐怕没有

77
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:24,520
Dozens of species of pollens have been discovered from the cretaceous era--
出土的白垩纪的样本也有许多的花粉了

78
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,550
how long ago was that?
那是多久以前了?

79
00:03:25,700 --> 00:03:27,870
65 million years.
6500万年

80
00:03:28,170 --> 00:03:30,020
That was a pretty good comeback.
