81
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:32,740
When authenticating a find like this, we have to be at the top of our game.
每次鉴定这种出土物, 我们必须掌控一切

82
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:36,490
Yeah,well,we all know that you're gonna say, "I am unable to authenticate with confidence."
行了, 我们都知道你要说 "我不能仅凭信心来做判定"

83
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:39,340
- Why would he do that? - When you declare something authentic,
- 何出此言？ - 当你想证明某事的时候

