00:03:39,470 --> 00:03:41,390
you run the risk of being proven wrong.
你会冒着被证实是错误的危险

85
00:03:41,510 --> 00:03:43,230
That doesn't happen if you equivocate.
当然如果你说话模棱两可就不会了

86
00:03:43,300 --> 00:03:44,260
As head of the jeffersonian,
作为Jeffersonian的领导

87
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:48,420
dr. Goodman will place the reputation of the institution over everything else.
Goodman博士会把机构的名声看得比什么都重

88
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,200
