我不知道你们之间刚才到底是怎么了

93
00:04:10,250 --> 00:04:12,800
Agent finn,why was the body removed from the crime scene?
Finn探员, 为什么尸体被从罪案现场移开?

94
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,360
Call me tricia, dr. Brennan.
叫我Tricia, Brennan博士

95
00:04:14,530 --> 00:04:17,960
The body was removed because parts were visible to arriving flights.
尸体被移开 是因为在航班到来时会被看到

96
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:20,370
Here's a map of the crime scene with a legend.
这是一张罪案现场的示意地图

97
00:04:20,520 --> 00:04:22,730
Now,there's a marked cone at the location of each body part,
在发现每一个尸体的地方都作了标记

98
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:25,050
